node.text: It's basically like a 12 minute risotto without the need to stir it. The easiest way to get even vegetable resistant kids to WANT to eat them because each bite has confetti like pieces of carrot and broccoli with tons of of flavors in every bite. What other vegetable would you want to add in? 🌶🫑 Recipe link in bio! https://weelicious.com/carrot-broccoli-cheese-orzo/

node.text: What kind of milk do you drink? I started making this homemade milk in different flavors (hello strawberry, chocolate and even green tea 🍵🍓🍫) and its been a game changer. Nothing but super creamy, plant-based milk you can use in cereal, coffee, smoothies, drink on it's own and much more. Recipe on Weelicious! https://weelicious.com/homemade-oat-milk-recipe/

node.text: Now that half of our family is vegetarian, I'm constantly trying to work on flexible recipes to fit everyone's food choices. These tacos are super California fresh and if you've never tried a crispy avocado, your life is about to change! Recipe on Weelicious. https://weelicious.com/whitefish-and-crispy-avocado-tacos-recipe/

BANANA BITES! 🍌🥞 Volume 🆙 Want to shake up pancakes in a way that’s kinda LIFE CHANGING? Just dip banana slices in Weelicious pancake batter (or any batter you love) and sauté them to create these addictive bites. It’s golden pancake surrounding a soft, caramelly banana center. Heaven in every bite! I add a little decadence by dipping them first in chocolate. What would you dip them in? 🍫🥜🍯🍁 Recipe link on Weelicious 💛⁣
⁣
https://weelicious.com/banana-bites/
